Package main.java.elsim.simulation.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSimEvent
    An abstract class defining some event occurring at a specific point in time during the simulation.
    CarMoveSimEvent
    Describes the elevator car moving to the next floor.
    DoorCloseSimEvent
    Describes the elevator car doors closing.
    DoorOpenSimEvent
    Describes the elevator car doors opening.
    PassengerArrivesAtFloorEvent  
    PassengerLeavesFloorSimEvent
    Describes a passenger's patience running out and leaving.
    PassengersEnterCarSimEvent
    Describes passengers entering the elevator car at a specific floor.
    PassengersExitCarSimEvent
    Describes passengers exiting the elevator at a specific floor.
